snippet.title: Tidewoken Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Tidewoken is a multiplayer turn-based combat strategy game with heavy focus on competitive and fair PvP, featuring over 200 unique skills.
Coming Late 2020 to Steam.

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1135220/Tidewoken/
Want to participate in the closed alpha? Join our Discord Server: https://discord.gg/hcR2m2R
Follow me on Twitter for daily updates: https://twitter.com/tidewoken
